OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry
OL,6,Fevening with some sunshine. The night
OL,7,Fwill then stay dry with long clear
OL,8,Fperiods, perhaps the odd mist or fog
OL,9,Fpatch around dawn.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FIt will be another fine dry
OL,12,Fday with plenty of sunshine though
OL,13,Fhigh cloud may turn the sunshine hazy
OL,14,Flater. Very warm with some cooling sea
OL,15,Fbreezes.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FBright
OL,18,Fand warm much of Friday, cloudier with
OL,19,Fchance of showers later. Saturday
OL,20,Fcloudy and cooler. Brighter with some
OL,21,Fsunshine on Sunday, but still cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
